criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women aged 18 to 36 with diagnosis of PCOS and insulin resistance or glucose
             intolerance.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Previous use of any hormonal treatment in the past three months;

          -  Other causes of anovulation;

          -  Gynecological or other associated conditions (endometriosis, adenomyosis or diabetes
             mellitus);

          -  FSH (Follicle Stimulating Hormone) > 15 Ul / L (2nd to 5th day of the cycle);

          -  Beta-hcG (human chorionic gonadotropin) positive (pregnancy).
